Title: Oubliette
Plot: Mulder seeks the help of a woman who he believes has a special connection with a young girl who has recently been kidnapped by the same man who held her captive many years earlier.
GuestStars: Tracey Ellis, Michael Chieffo, Jewel Staite, Ken Ryan, Dean Wray, Jacques LaLonde, David Fredericks, Sidonie Boll, Robert Underwood, Dollie Scarr, Bonnie Hay, Alexa Mardon, Eryn Collins
